Interface ISubjectManagementServer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ISubject<ITree<IProduct>>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ManagementServer

    public interface ISubjectManagementServer
extends ISubject<ITree<IProduct>>
    Specific interface for a ManagementServer subject. It binds the generic type of the ISubject interface to ITree parametrized with IProduct. This interface does not redefine any methods and is only introduced to make handling easier.
